| df+1+3 || h || 30? || 12 || KND || KND || KND || Counts as a command grab so must be broken with 1. Decent oki options afterwards too&lt;br /&gt;
|- &lt;br /&gt;
| df+2+4 || h || 30? || 12 || KND || KND || KND || Counts as a command grab so must be broken with 2. Decent oki options afterwards too&lt;br /&gt;
