==== Special Cancel Counterhit Combos ====&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
* 1, f,d,df+1&lt;br /&gt;
* d+1, f,d,df+1&lt;br /&gt;
* d+1, qcb+3 (depends on spacing and the opponent's character)&lt;br /&gt;
* 1,1,f,d,df+2&lt;br /&gt;
