* 1,1&lt;br /&gt;
* 2,2&lt;br /&gt;
* d+3&lt;br /&gt;
* b+4&lt;br /&gt;
* d+1&lt;br /&gt;
* ws+1&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
