=== Special cancelable moves ===&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
These are moves that can cancel into her special moves. You have to input the special move during the activation frames of the special cancelable move so you can't easily hit confirm.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
