&lt;br /&gt;
* df+2,3, b+2,3, b+4-&amp;gt;qcb+1 TS! fff+3, b+4 -&amp;gt; f,d,df+2&lt;br /&gt;
* f,f+3,4, fff+3, b+1,2,4&lt;br /&gt;
* b+4 -&amp;gt; f,d,df+1, b+2,3, b+4 -&amp;gt; qcb+1 TS! fff+3, b+4- -&amp;gt; f,d,df+2&lt;br /&gt;
