|-&lt;br /&gt;
|d+3, 2||l (TC), m||12,10||16||-13~-11||Launch (JG?)||Launch (JG?)|| Good CH launcher and relatively safe for a mid launcher. Since it high crushes, its good for dealing with high strings.&lt;br /&gt;
|-&lt;br /&gt;
