|-&lt;br /&gt;
|u/f+2, 1||m, m||10,10||18||-13||BU||KND?|| Your go to launcher. Since it will launch crouchers (unlike df+2) and its hit confirmable... you even get a bit of a mixup if they block the first hit. If they try to punish it and you finish the string, you get a CH launch.&lt;br /&gt;
