Staple: db+2, SSR deep qcf+1, df+3,2~f WS+1, iWS+1, iWS+1, iWS+1, f+1+2 - 71&amp;lt;br /&amp;gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Failsafe: db+2, dash qcf+1, df+1, df+3,2~f WS+1, qcf+4,2,3 - 69 Arguably this should be used as staple here.&amp;lt;br /&amp;gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;lt;br /&amp;gt;&lt;br /&gt;
uf+1&amp;lt;br /&amp;gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Staple: uf+1, CC df+3,2~SSR+1~f WS+1, iWS+1, iWS+1, iWS+1,1+2 S!, WR+1+2 - 70&amp;lt;br /&amp;gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Failsafe: uf+1, dash uf+3, df+1, d+2,3 S! dash qcf+4,2,3 - 64&amp;lt;br /&amp;gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;lt;br /&amp;gt;&lt;br /&gt;
CH f+2,1,4&amp;lt;br /&amp;gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Staple/failsafe: f+2,1,4, dash qcf+1, df+3,2~f WS+1, qcf+4,2,3 - 76 (Found no good iWS+1 alternative here)&amp;lt;br /&amp;gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&amp;lt;br /&amp;gt;&lt;br /&gt;
